Author: Starscream <starscream@flying-dice.com>
Date:   Sat May 9 13:26:44 2026 +0000

    feat(abt): replace SQLite with per-flow JSON store

    Implements specs/json-flow-store.md. Each flow now persists as a single
    JSON document at .abt/flows/{flow-id}.json holding metadata, snapshot,
    cursor, phase, timestamps, and both scopes.

    - Drops src/db.ts, replaces with src/paths.ts (constants + ensureDir)
    - Replaces FlowRepo/LocalRepo/GlobalRepo with a single FlowStore
    - Atomic writes via temp + rename to address partial-write risk
    - Internal node-tracking keys use __ separator instead of dots so
      parent/child paths (e.g. _node_status.1 and _node_status.1.0) no
      longer collide in the new nested object layout
    - All 3 existing flows migrated; SQLite files removed
    - Test suite path corrected from examples/ to .abt/trees/
    - 3/3 tests pass; tsc baseline unchanged

    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

